Install Ubuntu
Get it on the network
Firewall setup (ufw) and add required ports (ufw allow proto tcp from any to any port 80,443)

#Kills CPU...
Install microk8s (sudo snap install microk8s --classic)
Enable services (sudo microk8s enable dashboard dns registry istio)
Start (microk8s kubectl get all --namespaces)
Set kubectl (alias mkctl="microk8s kubectl)
Access Dashboard (microk8s dashboard-proxy)
Starting and Stopping (microk8s start/stop)

#Set up git
Clone repo: git clone <https target>
Cache PAT: git config --global credential.helper store


